cleaned_text: Welcome to Integrated Medicine, LLC A Center for Practitioners of Chiropractic, Naturopathic Medicine, and other holistic healthcare providers. Integrated Medicine LLC is a facility where like minded, holistic health care providers share space and offer private services such as Naturopathic medical care, Chiropractic care, mental health counseling, acupuncture and more.
